OL,3,CMan who died in Hartlepool collision
OL,4,Cfollowing police chase named
OL,6,FA man who died in a collision in
OL,7,FHartlepool following a police pursuit
OL,8,Fhas been named.
OL,10,FDuane Michael Birdsall, 44, lost his
OL,11,Flife when the blue VW Golf he was
OL,12,Fdriving collided with a concrete
OL,13,Fbollard at the junction of Elizabeth
OL,14,FWay and Tees Road in the early hours
OL,15,Fof Tuesday (7 April).
OL,17,FCleveland Police has referred itself
OL,18,Fto the Independent Office for Police
OL,19,FConduct.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
