OL,3,CMan who died in Hartlepool collision
OL,4,Cfollowing police chase named
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the force have said a 42-
OL,7,Fyear-old woman who was injured in the
OL,8,Fcollision has now been arrested and
OL,9,Fcharged with robbery in connection
OL,10,Fwith an incident the same morning.
OL,12,FShe appeared before Teesside
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday (8
OL,14,FApril), and was remanded in custody
OL,15,Funtil her next court appearance on 5
OL,16,FMay.
OL,18,FA 34-year-old man who suffered serious
OL,19,Finjuries in the collision remains in
OL,20,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
